config.comments: Process date is set by default to ETL_process_date context parameter.

entry.value: select * from FLOWFILE where completed = pipelines_count
select * from FLOWFILE where failed = 0 and completed < pipelines_count

SELECT ${pipelines_count} AS pipelines_count, count(CASE WHEN state = 'SCHEDULED' THEN 0 END) AS scheduled, count(CASE WHEN state = 'RUNNING' THEN 0 END) AS now_running, count(CASE WHEN state = 'FAILED' THEN 0 END) AS failed, count(CASE WHEN state = 'COMPLETED' THEN 0 END) AS completed FROM (SELECT state FROM ( SELECT *, max(modified_datetime) OVER (PARTITION BY component_name, process_date) AS max_modified_datetime FROM etl_traffic_lights WHERE process_date = ${process_date} ) etl_max WHERE component_name IN (${pipelines_names}) AND modified_datetime = max_modified_datetime) state_summary

entry.value: insert into Suggested_Product_STG_Push (dm_id, proposal_dm_id, create_datetime, update_datetime) select dm_id, proposal_dm_id, now(), now() from Suggested_Product p WHERE NULLIF(price_item_id, '') IS NOT NULL ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE proposal_dm_id = p.proposal_dm_id, update_datetime = now()

SELECT sp.dm_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}dm_id__c, simulation_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}simulation_Id__c, coalesce(market_product_type_id,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}market_product_type__c , coalesce(format_id,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Format__c, coalesce(price_item_id,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}priceItem__c, coalesce(quantity,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Quantity__c, coalesce(unit_of_measure_media_type,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}unit_of_measure__c, coalesce(list_price,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}List_Price__c, coalesce(total_net_price,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Total_Net_Price__c, coalesce(discount,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}disc__c, coalesce(`length`,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Lenght__c, coalesce(score,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}score__c, coalesce(inventory_available,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}inventory_available__c, coalesce(commercial_audience,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}commercial_audience__c, coalesce(market_funnel,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}campaign_objective_name__c, coalesce(avg_lines ,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}avg_lines_per_media__c, coalesce(gads_bidding_strategy,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Bidding_Strategy__c, coalesce(ttd_kpi,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}KPI__c, coalesce(ttd_target_value,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Target__c, coalesce(base_bid,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Base_Bid__c, coalesce(max_bid,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Max_Bid__c, coalesce(media_perc,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Cross_media__c, coalesce(third_party_product,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Third_Party__c, coalesce(adops_system_id,'#N/A') AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Ad_Ops_System_ID__c, sp.proposal_dm_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Suggested_Proposal__rDOTdm_id__c, 'true' #{Salesforce_Prefix}IsValid__c FROM Suggested_Product_STG_Push ssp, Suggested_Product sp WHERE sp.dm_id = ssp.dm_id UNION ALL SELECT ssp.dm_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}dm_id__c, '#N/A' AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}simulation_Id__c, market_product_type_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}market_product_type__c , format_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Format__c, price_item_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}priceItem__c, quantity AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Quantity__c, unit_of_measure_media_type AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}unit_of_measure__c, list_price AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}List_Price__c, total_net_price AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Total_Net_Price__c, discount AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}disc__c, `length` AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Lenght__c, score AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}score__c, inventory_available AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}inventory_available__c, commercial_audience AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}commercial_audience__c, market_funnel AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}campaign_objective_name__c, avg_lines AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}avg_lines_per_media__c, gads_bidding_strategy AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Bidding_Strategy__c, ttd_kpi AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}KPI__c, ttd_target_value AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Target__c, base_bid AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Base_Bid__c, max_bid AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Max_Bid__c, media_perc AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Cross_media__c, third_party_product AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Third_Party__c, adops_system_id AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Ad_Ops_System_ID__c, null AS #{Salesforce_Prefix}Suggested_Proposal__rDOTdm_id__c, 'false' #{Salesforce_Prefix}IsValid__c FROM Suggested_Product_STG_Push ssp LEFT JOIN Suggested_Product sp on(sp.dm_id=ssp.dm_id) WHERE sp.dm_id is null

SELECT coalesce(simulation_id,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}simulation_id__c, coalesce(advertiser_id,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}advertiser__c, coalesce(brand_id,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}brand__c, coalesce(start_date,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}From__c, coalesce(end_date,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}To__c, coalesce(audience,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}Commercial_Audience_Name__c, coalesce(objective,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}campaign_objective_name__c, coalesce(avg_daily_budget,'#N/A') as #{Salesforce_Prefix}Avg_budget__c, sp.dm_id as #{Salesforce_Prefix}dm_id__c, 'true' #{Salesforce_Prefix}IsValid__c from Suggested_Proposal sp, Suggested_Proposal_STG_Push ssp where sp.dm_id=ssp.dm_id UNION ALL SELECT '#N/A' as #{Salesforce_Prefix}simulation_id__c, advertiser_id as #{Salesforce_Prefix}advertiser__c, brand_id as #{Salesforce_Prefix}brand__c, '#N/A' as #{Salesforce_Prefix}From__c, '#N/A' as #{Salesforce_Prefix}To__c, audience as #{Salesforce_Prefix}Commercial_Audience_Name__c, objective as #{Salesforce_Prefix}campaign_objective_name__c, avg_daily_budget as #{Salesforce_Prefix}Avg_budget__c, ssp.dm_id as #{Salesforce_Prefix}dm_id__c, 'false' #{Salesforce_Prefix}IsValid__c from Suggested_Proposal_STG_Push ssp left join Suggested_Proposal sp on(sp.dm_id=ssp.dm_id) where sp.dm_id is null
